pullrequest.title: Use latest version of subt tunnel staging area

content.raw:
We found an issue downloading the latest model \(omitting the version in the `.sdf`\). The `subt_tunnel_staging_area` model was downloaded from Fuel \(after removing it from my local cache\), tagged as version 3, but the content wasn't version 3. Modifying the `.sdf` to explicitly download version 3 works as a workaround.

And the inside of the tunnel looks good to me in the right version.
